#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.175"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.175:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.175:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga "
msgstr "18. Intention "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: upavānasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.175:0.3"
msgid "175. Upavāṇasutta "
msgstr "175. With Upavāṇa "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: upavāṇo → upavāno (bj)
msgctxt "an4.175:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā upavāṇo yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā sāriputtena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Upavāṇa went up to Venerable Sāriputta, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an4.175:1.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā upavāṇo āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Upavāṇa sat down to one side, and said to Sāriputta: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.175:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, vijjāyantakaro hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, do you become a terminator because of knowledge?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.175:3.1"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“That’s not it, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.175:4.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, caraṇenantakaro hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Do you become a terminator because of conduct?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.175:5.1"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“That’s not it, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.175:6.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, vijjācaraṇenantakaro hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Do you become a terminator because of both knowledge and conduct?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.175:7.1"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“That’s not it, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.175:8.1"
msgid "“Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, aññatra vijjācaraṇenantakaro hotī”ti? "
msgstr "“Do you become a terminator for some reason other than knowledge and conduct?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.175:9.1"
msgid "“No hidaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“That’s not it, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.175:10.1"
msgid "“‘Kiṃ nu kho, āvuso sāriputta, vijjāyantakaro hotī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, when asked whether you become a terminator because of knowledge or conduct or knowledge and conduct, or for some other reason, "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.2"
msgid "‘no hidaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr "you say ‘that’s not it’. "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.3"
msgid "‘Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, caraṇenantakaro hotī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.4"
msgid "‘no hidaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.5"
msgid "‘Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, vijjācaraṇenantakaro hotī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.6"
msgid "‘no hidaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.7"
msgid "‘Kiṃ panāvuso sāriputta, aññatra vijjācaraṇenantakaro hotī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.8"
msgid "‘no hidaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.175:10.9"
msgid "Yathā kathaṃ panāvuso, antakaro hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How then do you become a terminator?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.164, sc11
msgctxt "an4.175:11.1"
msgid "“Vijjāya ce, āvuso, antakaro abhavissa, saupādānova samāno antakaro abhavissa. "
msgstr "“Reverend, if you became a terminator because of knowledge, then even someone who still has grasping could be a terminator. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.2"
msgid "Caraṇena ce, āvuso, antakaro abhavissa, saupādānova samāno antakaro abhavissa. "
msgstr "If you became a terminator because of conduct, then even someone who still has grasping could be a terminator. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇena ce, āvuso, antakaro abhavissa, saupādānova samāno antakaro abhavissa. "
msgstr "If you became a terminator because of both knowledge and conduct, then even someone who still has grasping could be a terminator. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.4"
msgid "Aññatra vijjācaraṇena ce, āvuso, antakaro abhavissa, puthujjano antakaro abhavissa. "
msgstr "If you became a terminator for some reason other than knowledge and conduct, then even an ordinary person could be a terminator. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.5"
msgid "Puthujjano hi, āvuso, aññatra vijjācaraṇena. "
msgstr "For an ordinary person lacks knowledge and conduct. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.6"
msgid "Caraṇavipanno kho, āvuso, yathābhūtaṃ na jānāti na passati. "
msgstr "Reverend, someone lacking good conduct does not know and see things as they are. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.7"
msgid "Caraṇasampanno yathābhūtaṃ jānāti passati. "
msgstr "Someone accomplished in good conduct knows and sees things as they are. "

msgctxt "an4.175:11.8"
msgid "Yathābhūtaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ antakaro hotī”ti. "
msgstr "Knowing and seeing things as they are, one is a terminator.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.175:11.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

